  "prompt": "How do you know if you have a crush on someone?",
  "response": "Having a crush on someone can manifest in various emotional and physical signs. Here are some common indicators that you might have a crush:\n\n### Emotional Signs:\n1. **Constant Thoughts**: You find yourself thinking about them frequently, even when you're trying to focus on other things.\n2. **Excitement and Nervousness**: You feel a mix of excitement and nervousness when you're around them or when you know you'll see them soon.\n3. **Happiness**: Just seeing them or thinking about them can make you feel happier.\n4. **Jealousy**: You might feel a twinge of jealousy if they spend time with other people or talk about other people positively.\n5. **Daydreaming**: You might find yourself daydreaming about scenarios where you interact with them or imagining a future together.\n\n### Physical Signs:\n1. **Butterflies**: You feel butterflies in your stomach when you're around them or thinking about them.\n2. **Blushing**: You might blush or feel your face get warm when they're near or when they talk to you.\n3. **Heart Rate**: Your heart might beat faster when you're around them or when you see them.\n4. **Sweaty Palms**: You might notice that your palms get sweaty when you're about to interact with them.\n\n### Behavioral Signs:\n1. **Seeking Their Attention**: You might go out of your way to get their attention or to be near them.\n2. **Trying to Impress**: You might dress nicer or act differently when you know you'll see them, trying to make a good impression.\n3. **Listening Intently**: You pay close attention to what they say and remember small details about their life.\n4. **Social Media Stalking**: You might find yourself frequently checking their social media profiles to see what they're up to.\n\n### Other Indicators:\n1. **Wanting to Know More**: You have a strong desire to learn more about them, their interests, and their life.\n2. **Feeling Inspired**: They might inspire you to be a better version of yourself or to pursue your own goals.\n3. **Sharing**: You want to share things with them, whether it's your thoughts, experiences, or even funny memes.\n\nRemember, having a crush is a normal part of human experience and can be a fun and exciting feeling. If you recognize these signs in yourself, it's likely you have a crush!",
